edu.brown.cs.systems.tracingplane.baggage_buffers

Class BaggageBuffers

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.systems.tracingplane.baggage_buffers.BaggageBuffers
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomLayer<BaggageBuffersContents>, BaggageLayer<BaggageBuffersContents>, TransitLayer<BaggageBuffersContents>

    public class BaggageBuffers
extends java.lang.Object
implements BaggageLayer<BaggageBuffersContents>

    The final layer in the baggage stack. BaggageBuffers is an implementation of the BaggageLayer. It enables you to register baggage-buffers compiled classes then access them through the generated accessor methods.
